---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Juan Pablo" description="About Juan Pablo Zamanillo">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About Juan Pablo"
				tagline="I’m a generative AI engineer and fiction writer in Sonoma, California. I build systems that learn to think in context. I write to dig for truth."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpeg"
					alt="Juan Pablo Zamanillo portrait"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
			  <h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
			  <div class="content">
			    <p class="mb-4">
					I’m Juan Pablo. I build generative AI and write fiction. My work lies where language meets emotion and systems.
			    </p>
		
			    <p class="mb-4">
					I started in natural language processing. For years, I helped teams find meaning in messy data—intelligence analysis, storytelling tools, you name it. These days, I care less about optimizing and more about being present. I build tools I trust. I write the stories I need to write.
			    </p>
			    <p class="mb-4">
					Sometimes you’ll find me leading an AI project. Sometimes I’m in a sunlit corner, Jessy nearby, writing. I keep chasing that spot where purpose meets presence. This site marks the trail.
			    </p>
			  </div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>I earned my M.S. in Data Science from American University, where I learned to see the world as patterns and questions. There, I built my base in statistics and machine learning, driven by a curiosity about language and how people connect. That’s where I learned to think in models and, more important, to ask the right questions.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I build generative AI systems. I design, deploy, and test them. Python, FastAPI, LangChain, and Hugging Face are my daily tools. I’ve run models in the cloud. I keep pipelines running with GitHub Actions and Docker. I lead with a clear mind and an eye for new ideas.
					</p>
					<p>
						I’m not just a coder. I see how systems fit together. I write. I fight for simple products.					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}

	.content p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
</style>
